Interface ISecurityPermissionChangeSet

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CreateEntity, CreateLink, EntityCreatedEvent, LinkCreatedEvent, SecurityDefinition, SecurityPermissionChangeEvent, SetItemSecurityPermissions

    public interface ISecurityPermissionChangeSet
    A set of security permissions to be applied to an Item by executing a command.
    Since:
    1.0

    • Method Summary
